      <table width="860" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0">
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baad3faee84e.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baad3faee84e.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-1 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13143.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13143.htm">神Ê軟chiá? [ SÎN Ê NŃG-CHIÁⁿ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">神&Ecirc;軟chi&aacute;ⁿ
 　　咱基督徒所信&ecirc;神是真軟chi&aacute;ⁿ &ecirc;神－據在人侮辱；予對敵歹款待，無ke講一句話，也無想欲報仇；尚且佇十字架頂來受見笑&ecirc;死。
　　無親像thang驚惶&ecirc;鬼將軍teh處治伊&ecirc;對敵，彼款&ecirc;神；也無親像大膽&ecirc;外科醫，無想患者&ecirc;艱苦，直刣、直割。反轉n&aacute;家己予人割&ecirc;款，會感著別人&ecirc;艱苦。
　　伊無親像強摃，摃破咱&ecirc;心門，強強入來。伊&ecirc;身軀予露水沃澹，徛佇門口teh細聲叫。伊無捲...<a href="artical-13143.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
